The study purpose is to observe which neoadjuvant chemotherapy regimens is the better for invasive breast cancer.

 The neoadjuvant chemotherapy regimen is sustained anthracyclines plus taxanes or from anthracyclines plus taxanes to vinorelbine plus cisplatinum.

